OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlind woman with ill baby  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdenied access to hospital  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman says she was refused access to 
OL,6, a west London hospital when she tried  
OL,7, to take her poorly baby inside for     
OL,8, treatment, because she had a guide dog.
OL,10,FHistorian and activist Dr Amy Kavanagh,
OL,11,F34, who is blind, was visiting West    
OL,12,FMiddlesex University Hospital.         
OL,14,FOn arrival, however, she says a        
OL,15,Fsecurity guard "kept shouting 'no dogs'
OL,16,Fat me and my partner" and patients and 
OL,17,Fstaff had to intervene.                
OL,19,FThe NHS trust says it is "taking this  
OL,20,Fincident seriously".                   
